{"tid":2023518,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"真孟德拉：Sometimes, it falls upon a generation to be great","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T05:42:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb9ec1df9d4180dbdfefbffc4d285deb1fded7ef","tid":2023518,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7OfnFC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7OfnFC.png&h=cddc9b57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3f4b6d672dbc8e097d5a3b48a1b63f27eef69aa","tid":2023518,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"真圖"},{"pid":"98b6721d67439d092c687d6bc7a27bdfed3fccd0","tid":2023518,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥剛表示要「認真研究如何監察網上假消息」，但散播假消息的，原來是她自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jEFyOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jEFyOd.png&h=1b7f3143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 自稱年年考第一、強調自己讀社會學的林鄭月娥，在記招為歷史教育爭議護航時，引述「南非總統孟德拉名言」：「教育的崩潰就是一個國家的崩潰 (The collapse of education is the collapse of the nation)」。<br />\n<br />\n2. 但翻查孟德拉語錄，他雖然有大量關於教育的論述，卻從沒有說過這一句話。這句話的中文版，明顯是互聯網「名人金句系列」隨便按上一個名人、配一句句子的那類fake news。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n3. 而首個出現這句「孟德拉名言」的媒體，是《文匯報》，反映林鄭月娥與國情接軌、在全球面前偽造真相的攬炒決心，異常堅定。</span></span></strong><br />\n(參見<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/257190475623742/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFinanceFellow%2Fphotos%2Fa.112035443472580%2F257190475623742%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=8a7c9f78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/257190475623742/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n4. 這句說話的出處，根據可查證資訊，據稱來自南非一名學者，據稱後來出現在南非大學入口，但全文意思同樣與林鄭月娥的穿鑿附會背道而馳。無論出自誰，前文後理很清楚，例如孟加拉報紙於此引述：&quot;Collapsing any nation does not require the use of atomic bombs or the use of long-range missiles. It only requires lowering the quality of education and allowing cheating in the examinations by the students&rdquo;. 也就是說，像新香港這樣，把教育質素降低、容許考試作弊，樂崩禮壞，就足以毀滅一個國家。<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.thedailystar.net/lifestyle/perspective/why-collapse-education-the-collapse-nation-1549213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Flifestyle%2Fperspective%2Fwhy-collapse-education-the-collapse-nation-1549213&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=cf429aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thedailystar.net/lifestyle/perspective/why-collapse-education-the-collapse-nation-1549213</a>)<br />\n<br />\n5. 究竟「真孟德拉」點睇教育？最出名係以下呢句，來自1997年，孟德拉為 Education Africa Presidential and Premier Education Awards 的發言：<br />\n<br />\n//The power of education extends beyond the development of skills we need for economic success. It can contribute to nation-building and reconciliation. Our previous system emphasized the physical and other differences of South Africans with devastating effects. We are steadily but surely introducing education that enables our children to exploit their similarities and common goals, while appreciating the strength in their diversity.//<br />\n<br />\n(<a href=\"http://www.mandela.gov.za/mandela_speeches/1997/971122_educ.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mandela.gov.za%2Fmandela_speeches%2F1997%2F971122_educ.htm&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=567ad0f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mandela.gov.za/mandela_speeches/1997/971122_educ.htm</a>) <br />\n<br />\n由此可見，真孟德拉深信教育的目的，並非機械性的把學生變成唯命是從、絕對服從、絕對忠誠、沒有討論空間的賺錢機器，更不是強調怎樣才是政治正確的南非種族主義教育可比。他認為教育對建立文明國家（特別是後種族隔離時代南非）具有重要功用，因為能令不同立場的人在開放、多元的社會無所畏懼地討論，不受文革式批鬥影響，明白社會和而不同的重要性，不但是教育釋放創造力的宗旨，也能促進大和解，令社會真正再出發。<br />\n<br />\n6. 至於孟德拉的個人理念，明顯也是林鄭月娥代表的價值觀的對立面。1964年，他被種族隔離政權審判時，有以下名言《我準備獻身》：&ldquo;I have cherished the ideal of a democratic and free society in which all persons live together in harmony and with equal opportunities. It is an ideal which I hope to live for and to achieve. But if needs be, it is an ideal for which I am prepared to die.&rdquo; 奧巴馬在孟德拉逝世後的悼詞，也有引述這句話。泉下有知，得知自己一生的精神，居然被林鄭月娥抽水，不知有何感想？<br />\n<br />\n7. 林鄭月娥的教育「哲學」，和杜撰出來的「孟德拉教育語錄」，都屬於由上而下的國家主義式觀念，更接近孟德拉批判的南非種族主義政權式教育，和孟德拉本人的教育理念、人生信仰，根本完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n8. 根據林鄭月娥「邏輯」，曲解孟德拉精神，在南非應該「沒有討論空間」。而在沒有民主、也沒有自由的新香港，林鄭月娥剛表示要「認真研究如何監察網上假消息」，但散播假消息的，原來是她自己。<br />\n<br />\n這就是後真相，這就是新香港。<br />\n<br />\n▶️「香港文革2.0」批鬥歷史試題，與「中國文革1.0」批鬥海瑞罷官<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39J-zgGp0Gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D39J-zgGp0Gk&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=46cb47ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39J-zgGp0Gk</a>"},{"pid":"d4be03e91f938bbcfc8bcfec6726e44750ae8262","tid":2023518,"uid":38646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"我讀社會學架<br />\n拍定手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef37796f57aebcfb330474dac3eae1d9766d92","tid":2023518,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d810eb9572c9a608923ba12b4a6ec16163c2c068","tid":2023518,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=91640fe1\" da